# General Rules

- Include the prompt used to create each change in a top-level directory called `prompts/`. Each file should be a markdown file named with the current date in ISO format followed by an incremented number padded with two zeroes, e.g. `2025-12-03-001.md`, `2025-12-03-002.md`, `2025-12-04-001.md`.
- Never change the contents of existing files in the prompts folder. Only create new files with incremented numbers.
- Give succinct answers.
